            "id": "HighRiskAssessment",
            "title": "Perform 5 year risk assessment",
            "description": "A 5 year risk assessment, either informal or formal using a validated instrument, will help determine if the patient may benefit from referral for high risk breast specialty evaluation.\n\nWomen at higher than average 5 year risk may be candidates for referral to breast specialist to discuss primary risk reduction interventions such as chemoprevention.",
